{"tid":1644411,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【黎明來到】美日支線任務再提醒我哋點樣贏啊！","createTime":"2019-10-10T14:13:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T21:31:01.000Z","uid":238693,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"500321cc287593883a0164e28ab15920739a8337","tid":1644411,"uid":238693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:13:17.000Z","msg":"多謝大陸憤青義和團上腦，引爆國際戰場支線任務<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />由Blizzard柒爆、South Park 串爆、NBA型爆甚至男兒當入樽嘅井上雄彥老師都支持香港，我哋夢寐以求三十年嘅國際圍堵中國終於成形<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />　我整理一下幾位國際重炮手嘅聲明，搵到香港文宣唔再捱打嘅方法，就係真正善用道德高地，叫人冇得反駁，想唔支持你都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先再睇返NBA CEO Adam Silver 講乜：<br />\n<em>&quot;<strong>Values of equality, respect and freedom of expression have long defined the NBA</strong> -- and will continue to do so.  As an American-based basketball league operating globally, among our greatest contributions are these values of the game.&quot;<br />\n&quot;Basketball runs deep in the hearts and minds of our two peoples.  At a time when divides between nations grow deeper and wider, we believe <strong>sports can be a unifying force that focuses on what we have in common as human beings</strong> rather than our differences.&quot;</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nba.com/article/2019/10/08/adam-silver-statement-china-nba\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nba.com%2Farticle%2F2019%2F10%2F08%2Fadam-silver-statement-china-nba&d=qlseXWlRX%2BAJHWkEdqgF5ZIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=90d160eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nba.com/article/2019/10/08/adam-silver-statement-china-nba</a><br />\n<br />\n平等、尊重多元、言論自由呢啲核心價值，邊有得反對？同埋成篇重點唔係鬧中國有幾衰，而係NBA 守護緊個個人都唔想失去嘅價值！你見耿爽班友越反駁越暴露自己窮得只有錢，就知呢個聲明有幾堅！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好啦再睇返人權女神Sharon Hom 個經典演說：<br />\n<em>&quot;Over the past three months, the whole world has witnessed a <strong>historic David and Goliath standoff</strong>. Against all odds, the Hong Kong people are standing up to the powerful, authoritarian regime in Beijing. In this historic battle, <strong>they are not only fighting for the democratic future of 7.4 million Hong Kong people, but they also holding the regional and global frontline on preserving human dignity and rights for all people&quot;</strong>.<br />\n</em><br />\n中間有好多直線抽擊去講大陸人權問題，回應美國國會疑問<br />\n<br />\n<em>This is what is happening on the ground. <strong>Hong Kong people are practicing democracy and exercising their freedoms for as long as possible. Hong Kongers are making the road by walking it.</strong> That is the real revolution already underway.</em><br />\n<br />\n結尾再強調返香港人有幾堅，革命唔單止係為咗懲罰中共，而係為咗守護美國同全球多數國家都不能反對嘅核心價值，萬世都不朽嘅民主與自由！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家搵唔搵到兩者共通點？道德高地唔係用嚟同手足割蓆，而係用黎凝聚支持力量，再令中立同反對嘅人口啞啞再出醜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我哋實際上可以做啲乜？我拋磚引玉希望大家一齊傾下再點改進：<br />\n<br />\n1. 文宣除咗譴責暴政同埋警暴，埋門一腳更要講清楚我哋守護緊啲乜，例如民主自由同埋公義法治！Vans, Blizzard, NBA 同 South Park 更加係一流文宣例子，去連結全世界本身對政治冷漠嘅大眾，例如早兩晚Twitch 洗版大戰，用埋SwiftRage FREE NBA SwiftRage FREE BLIZZARD SwiftRage FREE HONG KONG就中晒外國gamer 關注啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 對街坊理論文宣就更要be water，例如好多街坊呻搞黨鐵影響民生，我哋唔好鑽入去齋講黨鐵有幾仆街，可以先講「咦我最近轉搭巴士重有位坐喎！」「不如即刻搵想選區議員個後生仔女一齊爭取加班次新路線！」「其實未示威都又出軌又故障，多啲巴士小巴分散風險咪重好？」，<strong>真正懲罰到黨鐵唔係罰錢，而係成個交通系統同城市發展模式唔撚再俾佢壟斷</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />　<br />\n<br />\n黑店被裝修都唔駛齋講福建幫有幾仆街，不妨先轉移視線「啊你記唔記得舊時附近間ＸＸ茶樓平靚正？」「變藥房之前行街買嘢舒服好多！」「ＣＹ生意好差咩？但係隔離間良心小店做到冇停手喎！」我哋要慢慢拉風，<strong>講清楚攬炒背後我哋係要建立個市場更公平，生活有尊嚴有選擇嘅經濟模式！</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同時間文宣可以再進化去強調有咩車搭嘅交通路線，再貼落黨鐵已封出口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，連儂牆除左行動post，不妨做多啲一人一間你想佢開返嘅小舖老店，衝出同溫層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！連同新職業圍觀師，引人圍觀再討論威力加倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好啦唔打咁多等大家一齊諗多啲可以做咩，小弟之前嘔心瀝血咁集合咗個21種職業人人有工開，借位推多次希望唔好咁快沉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一齊盡做嬴埋佢！<br />\n<br />\n【突破革命樽頸攻略2.0】和理勇加到21個職業，人人有工開！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ekdatS\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ekdatS</a>"},{"pid":"0d756dc5a1902580e68a6a8940962e0b8bcbdd68","tid":1644411,"uid":293227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:14:29.000Z","msg":"撥行個國際戰火呀手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大直路呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"435e10c3d75b9472d8e711b60c076406eb4f3f52","tid":1644411,"uid":238693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d756dc5a1902580e68a6a8940962e0b8bcbdd68","tid":1644411,"uid":293227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:14:29.000Z","msg":"撥行個國際戰火呀手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大直路呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:17:59.000Z","msg":"等撚咗三十幾年啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef27f4504df66aff0f5d0f89309542ac5b54f0a","tid":1644411,"uid":238693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:22:44.000Z","msg":"今次要羸返次！"},{"pid":"128f65280e362d127c926a9ac86af5630054dde2","tid":1644411,"uid":62816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:22:50.000Z","msg":"巴打好高汁，和理非絕對可跟<br />\n獅鳥又不了，跳閘又唔敢，裝修又暴力，戴口罩又怕俾狗逗<br />\n好，依家玩語言藝術拉攏港豬無曬藉口喇嘛？<br />\ngo啦和理非！！！<br />\n推呀！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb90494291bee64933ffaef69eb401af12d2154d","tid":1644411,"uid":2607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:24:38.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"fb2f793b2d2faf69c357f252b9fea9a1d55b6768","tid":1644411,"uid":228938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:24:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e47e2990fc8450480fd874824bffbfba16205e98","tid":1644411,"uid":2607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"128f65280e362d127c926a9ac86af5630054dde2","tid":1644411,"uid":62816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:22:50.000Z","msg":"巴打好高汁，和理非絕對可跟<br />\n獅鳥又不了，跳閘又唔敢，裝修又暴力，戴口罩又怕俾狗逗<br />\n好，依家玩語言藝術拉攏港豬無曬藉口喇嘛？<br />\ngo啦和理非！！！<br />\n推呀！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:27:27.000Z","msg":"休完幾日好做野"},{"pid":"8e8a6ebe2317e38ca290e848af3c7d4b069c2165","tid":1644411,"uid":66546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:31:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77018990d1878b3c5fa71a7c960841f165ec8861","tid":1644411,"uid":3776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:31:35.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"2096594633160fd35c77e1ed750ce174d3af610e","tid":1644411,"uid":145884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:55:24.000Z","msg":"[行動post]如何塞鐵<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ekPgwS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ekPgwS</a>"},{"pid":"29b4b4477cc47ea4989560a3e76b5062b4ae10c3","tid":1644411,"uid":37058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:59:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e28ab