=30109389\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191010%2F59977856&h=ea3c09ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191010/59977856</a>"},{"pid":"4be79abbd38f2a642ec5514db9d0629c9ed1cdf4","tid":1644411,"uid":325214,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:06:38.000Z","msg":"五六日<br />\n為自由而戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K49Kk5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK49Kk5a.jpg&h=b1f6b77c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb0871ac5f96582e8f7ddb25e98b9e3281130e4e","tid":1644411,"uid":62816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:09:42.000Z","msg":"高汁文要推！"},{"pid":"7c15566f71a75293bf66cc679d7b5d67fffbeef7","tid":1644411,"uid":238693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:12:11.000Z","msg":"唉打咁耐都唔夠謝sir 啲post 嚟，大家可以幫手推多啲嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f105b32e78c86de72750dff2477710a7b7ffe35","tid":1644411,"uid":266081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:21:17.000Z","msg":"我鍾意搭車時出口術用whatsapp語音教通識學生咩係政府認受性理論，同埋同我阿媽講邊間鋪頭好食、講下香港少左遊客同水貨佬令條街舒服好多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f004dd786e6a344a41fa9c9f73fd6055d6f00b67","tid":1644411,"uid":238693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T15:26:24.000Z","msg":"【推特瘋傳】近日推特瘋傳，不同族裔，不同國家，用廣東話撐香港。香港人不孤單。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/57D3JKSk9js\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F57D3JKSk9js&d=qlseXWlRX%2BAJHWkEdqgF5ZIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=e5936606\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/57D3JKSk9js</a>"},{"pid":"7349217e3b4e736876e7985bc75d0c2abfab0035","tid":1644411,"uid":